    <date day="03" month="November" year="2024"></date>
    <abstract>
      <t>   This draft updates [RFC7518] to deprecate the JWS algorithm "none"
   and the JWE algorithm "RSA1_5".  These algorithms have known security
   weaknesses.

	 </t>
